at the scattered tiny remains.  Her tears flowed for them all.

"This is great.  I havent done this since I was a kid, this is the 
best."  Together. Friends.  " Yes, you bring out the more spontaneous 
side in me too."  "Really? Erm, well hey, we dont know what will 
